<function>

access:  static public

name: pathinfo

param: int, $key, NULL

param: mixed, $default, NULL

return: mixed

</function>

Safely gets the value of $_SERVER['PATH_INFO'] element.

* Parameters:

 * int //$key//: The array element; if null, returns the whole array.

 * mixed //$default//: If the requested array element is not set, return this value.

* Returns mixed: The array element value (if set), or the $default value (if not).